data.description: *MOTIVATED SELLERS* Sellers are willing to pay $5000 towards buyers closing cost with an acceptable offer. Nicely updated kitchen with shaker cabinets, and engineered hardwood floors throughout main level. Open floor plan, great for entertaining guests. Primary on the main level with updated full bath, powder bath and spacious walk-in closet, along with 2 bedroom upstairs with full bath. Recreational room with potential in-law suite and full bath downstairs. Newer roof, water heater and HVAC. Freshly stained and painted front and back porch! Brand new concrete patio outback for grilling! Beautiful, partially wooded backyard for quiet evenings by the fire. Schedule your showing TODAY! Agent related to seller.
